        2017 as a hobby. I have done lotâ€™s to things with lot of technology. I
        have nothing much to show till yet but i have done lot of work for
        startup's and friends . I will not bore you with my talk to much if you
        want to read more about me
        <a href="/about">click here</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Recent Post's</h2>
      <ul class="posts">
        {
          posts.map((post) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/blog/${post.slug}/`}>
                <p class="title">{post.data.title}</p>
              </a>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
      <div>
        <a href="/blogs">Show More</a>
      </div>

      <p>
        My post are also availble at:
        <ul>
          <li>
